\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

x |+| y |+| z
\end_layout

\end_inset

 does not depend on the choice of parentheses: 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

(x |+| y) |+| z == x |+| (y |+| z)
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 This makes programs written using the semigroup operation 
\begin_inset listings
inline true
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

|+|
\end_layout

\end_inset

