\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 Formally, a type 
\begin_inset Formula $T$
\end_inset

 is a monoid when there is an associative binary operation 
\begin_inset Formula $\oplus_{T}$
\end_inset

 and a chosen 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

empty
\begin_inset Quotes erd
