 The first line above:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(a+\bbnum 0\right)\oplus\left(e_{A}+\bbnum 0\right)=a+\bbnum 0\quad,\quad\quad\left(e_{A}+\bbnum 0\right)\oplus\left(a+\bbnum 0\right)=a+\bbnum 0\quad,
\]

\end_inset

