\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

  : Pointed[Lambda[X => F[G[X]]]]
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

  = Pointed[Lambda[X => F[G[X]]]](implicitly[Pointed[F]].pure[F, G[Unit]](implici
tly[Pointed[G]].wu))     
\end_layout

\end_inset

The case when 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $G$
\end_inset

