\begin_inset Formula $C^{\bbnum 1}$
\end_inset

 to compute a value of type 
\begin_inset Formula $F^{C^{\bbnum 1}}$
\end_inset

.
 So, 
\begin_inset Formula $F\circ C$
\end_inset

 is pointed whenever both 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $F$
\end_inset

